<Author>jibaro2275
<Content>Do not waste your time or money Got fool by the web site pictures. live and learn, never again book one of these small hotels thru the web.Anyway we have 4 kids with us from 25 to 13 yrs traveling around PR and learnig about this beautiful island have to offer. When we got to The Cofresi Beach Club Hotel our kids said to us that they feel weird and uncomfortable in the room. The hotel was empty and we (my wife and I) went downstairs, after driving for 4 hrs ,and explained the situation with the kids to the manager and to ask for a refund. They refused and we decided not to pursue and left. The rooms were old and not kept up, we went to see the roof pool and laughed, our bath tub is the same size , that was the best joke of the day.Anyway if your are really drunk and prefer to sleep someplace else than the street call them. 
