<Content>Great Place to stay!!!! Great place to stay. Clean and comfortable. Great pricing for the off season. The staff was extra friendly. Couldn't ask for better. Right down the street from the poblado (village) of Boqueron. What an amazing place. Everyone is friendly and Sundays nights are the best down there. The hotel is convienent to everywhere in Puerto Rico with the small town atmosphere. LOVE IT will stay there again. 
